Package: openerp-client
Architecture: all
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, python, python-egenix-mxdatetime, python-glade2, python-gtk2
Conflicts: tinyerp-client (<< 5.0.0~alpha-2)
Replaces: tinyerp-client
Recommends: python-matplotlib, openoffice.org-writer, evince | pdf-viewer
Suggests: openerp-server
Description: Enterprise Resource Management (client)
 OpenERP is a complete ERP and CRM. The main features are accounting (analytic
 and financial), stock management, sales and purchases management, tasks
 automation, marketing campaigns, help desk, POS, etc. Technical features
 include a distributed server, flexible workflows, an object database, a dynamic
 GUI, customizable reports, and NET-RPC and XML-RPC interfaces.
 .
 This package contains the OpenERP client, install openerp-server package for
 the server.

Package: tinyerp-client
Architecture: all
Depends: openerp-client
Description: Enterprise Resource Management (client; transitional package)
 Package to ease upgrading from older tinyerp-client packages to the new
 openerp-client package.
 .
 This package can be purged at anytime once the openerp-client package has been
 installed.
